CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784074689
OL,3,C'Landmark' study to see blood test for
OL,4,CAlzheimer's offered by GPs
OL,6,FPeople suspected of having Alzheimer's
OL,7,Fdisease will now be able to get a
OL,8,Fblood test for the condition through
OL,9,Ftheir GP, as part of a "landmark"
OL,10,Fstudy taking place in Scotland.
OL,12,FMore than 50 GPs in central and
OL,13,Fnorthern Scotland are taking part in
OL,14,Fthe study, which is called Bringing
OL,15,FAlzheimer's Disease Biomarkers to
OL,16,FGeneral Practice (BriDGe).
OL,26,@qD@XOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
